[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/light_screen">Light Screen</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A wondrous wall of light is put up to suppress damage from special attacks for five turns.</p>